BELDEN, Appellant, v. BURKE et al., Respondents. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. December 15, 1893.) Action by James J. Belden against Stevenson Burke and others.

Argued before VAN BRUNT, P. J., and FOLLETT and PARKER, JJ.

Elihu Root, for appellant. Jas. W. Hawes, for respondents.

No opinion. Motion denied, with $10 costs. See 20 N. Y. Supp. 320; 25 N. Y. Supp. 601.
